**`.gitignore`** — also add to your project root:
```
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
venv/
.env

# Database
*.db
*.sqlite3

# ML models (large files)
backend/ml/saved_models/*.pkl

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
```

